術領先全球"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:04:33.000Z","msg":"全能到仆街 偷拍技術都咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b358748f327b17639caea3a6d49bd78715fc25","tid":1008010,"uid":165359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b44ca54fd554d4defebd50e40c671969aae24196","tid":1008010,"uid":153329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"女人去廁所都唔係淨係柯尿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"D女人好撚古惑架"},{"pid":"9e28cdf97f761f0d6594bac871581cc60e52222c","tid":1008010,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}